The action takes place 20 years before the events Halo: Combat Evolved. Cruiser Spirit of Fire, sent to the United Nations Space Command (OSCC), ordered to investigate and stop the action on the planet Harvest,i.e Covenant (the place of first contact with aliens). Learning about the mysterious excavation covenants under the leadership of the unknown prophet, Captain James Cutter sends his soldiers to find out what happens.

